title: Berserk Rampage
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

For every successful To Hit roll that [[Old One Eye]] makes in close combat (excluding those from its [[thresher scythe|Thresher Scythe]]), it may immediately make one additional Attack against the same unit. These additional Attacks do not confer extra Attacks.